TextBody:
HI Mohamed,

Thank you for your time today!
As stated, I manged to track down the issue internally.
To be more specific- Effective rights report might generate the wrong rights being shown(i.e, a user having no rights/denied, and being displayed as allowed)
A fix for this is being targeted in the next version release, so 5.9.4.0 which should not be too far away.
I will leave the case opened meanwhile, and do get back here with updates, after the server version gets released and you apply the patch and retest the scenario.


Adrian Stanca
Technical Support Engineer

DLP | Device Control | Content Aware Protection | Enforced Encryption | eDiscovery
Email | Website | LinkedIn
